;">Hi friends &#128075;,</p><p style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; li=
ne-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Happy Monday! This is an essay I&#821=
7;ve been thinking about and working on for a little while &#8211; I quote =
