e since the beginning of Not Boring &#8211; and I&#8217;m really excited to=
 share it with you. It&#8217;s as close to a Theory of Everything as I can =
come up with to understand the world in 2022.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: #=
404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>Once=
 I started thinking about the world this way, I&#8217;ve seen it pop up eve=
