#404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">And as I&=
#8217;ve tried to explain it to people, I&#8217;ve realized that I just nee=
d to write down as coherent a thesis with as much evidence as I can, and op=
en it up to get feedback and pushback. If nothing else, I hope it can be an=
 interesting conversation starter at Thanksgiving dinner on Thursday.</p><p=
 style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 2=
0px 0;">The idea is this: the world oscillates between centralization and d=
ecentralization, with progress sloping upward through the turns. We&#8217;r=
e approaching an era of decentralization.</p><p style=3D"color: #404040; fo=
nt-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">An important note on=
 how you should set expectations going into this piece:&#160;</p><ul style=
