ial-format: bullet;"><p style=3D"box-sizing: border-box; color: #404040; fo=
nt-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-left=
: 4px;"><span>You </span><strong>should not</strong><span> read this as a b=
ull case for crypto. While the word &#8220;decentralization&#8221; is tied =
